Start Simple: Begin by building core functionalities like connecting your bot to your Discord server and responding to basic commands (e.g., "!help" to display a list of commands).

**Features**
Character creation and customization
Leveling up system
Quests and missions
Combat mechanics
Inventory management
Social interaction commands
Guilds or factions
Leaderboards or rankings

**COMMANDS TO MAKE**

*starting*
Awake           -       Awake and become a hunter!
Choose class    -       Choose a permanent class
Profile	        -       Show your profile or other hunter's profile
Inventory	    -       Show your inventory